Package org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.cte

Support for SqmMutationStrategy implementations that use CTE (SQL's Common Table Expression) approach to perform the update/delete

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCteMutationHandler
    Defines how identifier values are selected from the updatable/deletable tables.

    CteDeleteHandlerImpl
